# PLAYER::GET_PLAYER_DEBUG_INVINCIBLE

## Summary
Gets if the player has debug invincible to all damage types

## Parameters
* **PLAYER_INDEX** player

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Always returns false.
